 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/772/floating-workspace/?answer=6654#post-id-6654</link><description>This does actually work as of i3 4.11, exactly with the syntax OP originally proposed:

    for_window [workspace="9"] floating enable 

That said, our attitude towards floating hasn't changed and don't recommend doing this. </description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Sep 2015 09:08:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/772/floating-workspace/?answer=6654#post-id-6654</guid></item><item><title>Answer by Michael for &lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
