 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/772/floating-workspace/?answer=773#post-id-773</link><description>No. Floating workspaces are evil as i3 is not a floating wm. Use tiling windows instead.</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Nov 2012 15:24:36 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/772/floating-workspace/?answer=773#post-id-773</guid></item><item><title>Comment by alex_geirby for &lt;p&gt;No. Floating workspaces are evil as i3 is not a floating wm. Use tiling windows instead.&lt;/p&gt;
